'''Geoffrey Pierson''' (born [[June 16]], [[1949]]) provided voices for the [[The Empire Strikes Back (radio)|Empire Strikes Back radio drama]], and later provided voices for ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''. For the radio drama, he provided the voice of [[Lobot/Legends|Lobot]], among other characters, making him the first actor to perform the voice of the [[Cloud City/Legends|Cloud City]] [[Cyborg/Legends|cyborg]].

